hey everyone

Brewers beat the cubbies today! 16-2 with 6 home runs! yay. 

so i had a very boring day today. yup... thats about it.


yesterday was pretty cool though.
after school i went with my bio/ap bio class to the gross anatomy lab at marquette. We had a cadaver lab field trip. it was really cool. i was nervous at first.... being around all the bodies. it was not what i expected. i got to touch the arm muscles and ligaments.... and a brain. it was pretty cool. the smell was the worst. 

The rooms have a hint of asbestos and maybe just a dash of formaldehyde.

well not the asbestos, but it reeked of formaldehyde. yeah. 
otherwise it was pretty awesome.




friday night i also went to brookfield square. I finally got my brewers jersey! yay.


and thats about all the highlights of my weekend.
yup



and a little advice....
Suck it up. life isnt always perfect. deal with it and grow up.

                                            das Ende

or start wearing blue and gold cause the brewers are playing right now. yes, you may call me obsessed, and yes... if you do i will tell you to fuck off, buddy. haha  The brewers are  amazing. i was freaking out last night cause the game was so exciting. it was crazyness!  so right now.. i am drinking a diet mt. dew, watching the brewers, and extremely happy that i finally got my nephew to sleep. i hate the "sister's obligation" to babysit without pay. arrgh i could have made millions by now. well not millions, but pretty darn close.
anywhoo i am in a kinda-bad mood cause i now cant go to the Matches concert next thursday. i saved up all my money and my mom still wont let me go. ahhhh the joys of having an over-protective mother. she said.... and  i quote "you can do whatever you want..... when you're 18" gah! how does that help me out now?!?!?! not to sound all emo and all but my mom does not understand how much i like music. wow that sounded almost too cliche`
ehh whatever.... i'll get used to it.
ahh i hope the brewers win the game!!! i almost had a heart attack from last nights game!
well i am gonna go relocate myself infront of the tv.... and hope that we keep the lead.



when life gives you lemons.... throw them at stupid people.
                                                 <3.lauren
